  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story Background:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >During its voyage, the submarine suddenly experienced a mechanical failure. Dr. Pierre hurriedly began investigating, only to find abnormal intrusions in every area.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Investigate cases in the azure abyss, and follow Dr. Pierre to uncover the secrets of the Nautilus.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2925090/extras/45789fce485fc83e4728cd56d86626cd.avif?t=1742492403\" width=616 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in the eerie atmosphere of the Nautilus, filled with secrets and unsettling anomalies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2925090/extras/d06deabffc943c2f140f5bdddfd11176.poster.avif?t=1742492403\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2925090/extras/d06deabffc943c2f140f5bdddfd11176.webm?t=1742492403\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2925090/extras/d06deabffc943c2f140f5bdddfd11176.mp4?t=1742492403\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2925090/extras/c9a87c6f3b034aa409ee03f6d5a7ec9f.avif?t=1742492403\" width=616 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience 2.5D deduction + puzzle gameplay, combine your observation skills to solve problems and navigate through various cabins.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2925090/extras/80511b44a54ee7a0f760f16ffb9c49a5.poster.avif?t=1742492403\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2925090/extras/80511b44a54ee7a0f760f16ffb9c49a5.webm?t=1742492403\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2925090/extras/80511b44a54ee7a0f760f16ffb9c49a5.mp4?t=1742492403\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2925090/extras/0d0abfe04ba8b1fae0c2ce84dfb32e5f.avif?t=1742492403\" width=616 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Many anomalies are hidden in the submarine, related to the time vortex. Can you unlock the secrets of time and space and escape the submarine?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2925090/extras/cdc016997b50e6d6e556f4ebe36134b5.poster.avif?t=1742492403\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2925090/extras/cdc016997b50e6d6e556f4ebe36134b5.webm?t=1742492403\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2925090/extras/cdc016997b50e6d6e556f4ebe36134b5.mp4?t=1742492403\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2925090/extras/0ece6200f9dae96665c7726054bbc58a.avif?t=1742492403\" width=616 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1866</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dr. Pierre, the owner of the Nautilus, and his seven sailors accidentally salvaged a \"compass\" during their voyage.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This compass allowed him to glimpse his true position in the universe. It also caused the Nautilus to sink into a time vortex.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2925090/extras/306bb2a22b499458a0ae43bf83e09a5b.poster.avif?t=1742492403\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2925090/extras/306bb2a22b499458a0ae43bf83e09a5b.webm?t=1742492403\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2925090/extras/306bb2a22b499458a0ae43bf83e09a5b.mp4?t=1742492403\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2998</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Su\" is a student from a future city. During an underwater trip, she encountered an ancient submarine trapped in time and space.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Su entered the submarine to explore but was captured by the time vortex into another unknown space-time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players play as Dr. Pierre.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Interacting with items marked with time stamps can penetrate time to obtain more clues.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore interesting \"time wormholes\" and various props to uncover the truth of the story.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p>",
